{"tid":1840990,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇諗過支那種當初點解少咗嚟香港？","createTime":"2020-01-25T05:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T10:02:59.000Z","uid":311193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc2a76c7156a363377a02510fc5b0143d18f907e","tid":1840990,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:52:29.000Z","msg":"TG?<br />\n抗爭者？<br />\n大遊行？<br />\n街頭戰爭？<br />\n定全民三罷？<br />\n我哋不斷叫醫護人員罷工 又真係淨係得把口叫人哋做嘢 自己就攤係張床打字或者自己返緊工<br />\n不如諗下可以做乜 係由我哋自己親手親腳令到減低支那種keep住落嚟<br />\n撤回逃犯條例都搞咗幾個月 又語言藝術 又帶我哋遊花園先肯真係答應撤回<br />\n不如係到傾我哋民間可以用咩方法解決<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己香港 自己救</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tywv9yL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftywv9yL.gif&h=025f84b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01f458e32c8d3f8f42e1a0605fdccbc00d0f722b","tid":1840990,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:53:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">傾行動post</span></strong>"},{"pid":"1a663c217c033bc9607a8082349874274f276b1d","tid":1840990,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">傾行動post</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e6b8892db1be36ffb60559534e8245c4eecbe299","tid":1840990,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:53:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">傾行動post</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e23c2365d7a8d05963ef9c3b8f5b5b88027e6770","tid":1840990,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:53:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">傾行動post</span></strong>"},{"pid":"644c89b51f4e0c00ee0db224026b81c0e06b0e13","tid":1840990,"uid":311193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T05:53:52.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">傾行動post</span></strong>"},